                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 3123/8.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Graves</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Stockholm</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1907-12-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 10, 1907</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(States that the funeral of the King of Sweden will take place on the 19th of
                    December, and that Great Britain, Germany, Austria, and other countries will be
                    represented by a member of the royal family. France will probably have special
                    representatives.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
